title: Hunter Active (~70)
comment_one:
*1 = Strength as needed for accuracy
*2 = Extra points here after Gilded and Axe are maxed and you hit accuracy needs
comment_two: Limbs and Veins for damage. Piercing arrow for clear
comment_three: After you max damage from items, start working on uwu rawrrr and traps. Goal is to get both to 100.
notes: With this build, you will likely have your best XP per hour at poops/rats. If you have enough damage, a spear might be better over a bow.
